Package org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.fsa

Class InputTester.AcceptingRunFinder

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.DFS
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.DoubleDFS
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.fsa.InputTester.AcceptingRunFinder
Enclosing class:
InputTester
static class InputTester.AcceptingRunFinder
extends DoubleDFS
This class is used to traverse a configuration automaton C of an automaton A to find a lasso of C such that the corresponding lasso of A is accepting.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
